

=Bio=

Project Manager and User Interface Designer for EveryVote.org. 

EveryVote.org's current projects:

EVmini- a Facebook, iOS, Android, and stand-alone platform where university students can learn about and interact with all of their student government candidates on one convenient webpage

EVomni- a comprehensive election information and government monitoring tool, where constituents can learn about, share their opinion on, compare their opinion with, and contact EVERY candidate they are eligible to vote for and EVERY elected official who represents them on one convenient webpage

Crew member aboard Spaceship Earth. I am passionate about advocating for and creating free (AGPL) and federation-compatible civic engagement software.

Some folks I'm inspired by: Marshall McLuhan, Joseph Campbell, Thomas Paine, Buckminster Fuller, Terence McKenna,  Robert Anton Wilson, David Foster Wallace, Alan Moore, Alan Watts, and a bunch of those Enlightenment thinkers...eek I should really add women to this list...


